quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  26,111,Unhon ne jawab diya “kya hum tujhey maan lein halaanke teri pairwi razil-tareen (lowest/meanest) logon ne ikhtiyar ki hai?”
  26,112,Nooh ne kaha “main kya jaanu ke unke amal kaise hain
  26,113,"Unka hisaab to mere Rubb ke zimme hai, kaash tum kuch shaoor se kaam lo"
  26,114,Mera yeh kaam nahin hai ke jo iman layein unko main dhutkaar doon
  26,115,Main to bas ek saaf saaf mutanabbeh (warn) kardene wala aadmi hoon”
  26,116,"Unhon ne kaha “Aey Nooh , agar tu baaz na aaya to phitkarey huey logon mein shamil hokar rahega”"
  26,117,"Nooh ne dua ki “Aey mere Rubb, meri qaum ne mujhey jhutla diya"
  26,118,Ab mere aur unke darmiyan do-toak faisla karde aur mujhey aur jo momin mere saath hain inko nijaat de”
  26,119,Aakhir e kaar humne usko aur uske saathiyon ko ek bhaari hui kashti mein bacha liya
  26,120,Aur uske baad baaqi logon ko garq (drown) kardiya
  26,121,"Yaqeenan ismein ek nishani hai, magar inmein se aksar log maanne waley nahin"
  26,122,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi
  26,123,Aad ne Rasoolon ko jhutlaya
  26,124,Yaad karo jabke unke bhai Hood ne unse kaha tha “kya tum darte nahin
  26,125,Main tumhare liye ek amaanat-daar Rasool hoon
  26,126,Lihaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,127,"Main is kaam par tumse kisi ajar ka talib nahin hoon, mera ajar to Rabbul Aalameen ke zimme hai"
  26,128,Yeh tumhara kya haal hai ke har unchey maqaam par la haasil ek yaadgaar imarat bana daalte ho
  26,129,Aur baday baday qasar (huge castles) taamir karte ho goya tumhein hamesha rehna hai
  26,130,Aur jab kisi par haath daalte ho jabbar ban kar daalte ho
  26,131,Pas tum log Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,132,Daro ussey jisne woh kuch tumhein diya hai jo tum jaante ho
  26,133,"Tumhein jaanwar diye, auladein di"
  26,134,Baagh diye aur chashme(water-springs) diye
  26,135,Mujhey tumhare haqq mein ek baday din ke azaab ka darr hai”
  26,136,"Unhon ne jawaab diya “ tu naseehat kar ya na kar, hamare liye yaksan hai"
  26,137,Yeh baatein to yunhi hoti chali aayi hain
  26,138,Aur hum azaab mein mubtala honay walay nahin hain”
  26,139,"Aakhir e kaar unhon ne usey jhutla diya aur humne unko halaak kardiya. Yaqeenan ismein ek nishani hai, magar inmein se aksar log maanne waley nahin hai"
  26,140,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi
  26,141,Samood ne Rasoolon ko jhutlaya
  26,142,Yaad karo jabke unke bhai Saleh ne unse kaha “kya tum darte nahin
  26,143,Main tumhare liye ek amaanat-daar Rasool hoon
  26,144,Lihaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,145,"Main is kaam par tumse kisi ajar ka talib nahin hoon, mera ajar to Rabbul aalameen ke zimme hai"
  26,146,"Kya tum un sab cheezon ke darmiyan, jo yahan hain, bas yunhi itminaan se rehne diye jaogey"
  26,147,In baaghon (gardens) aur chasmon mein
  26,148,In kheton aur nakhlistano (date-groves) mein jinke khosey rass bharey hain
  26,149,Tum pahad khodh khodh kar fakhariya (proudly) un mein imaratein banate ho
  26,150,Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,151,Un bay-lagaam logon ki itaat na karo
  26,152,Jo zameen mein fasaad barpa karte hain aur koi islaah nahin karte”
  26,153,Unhon ne jawab diya “tu mehaz ek sehar-zadah (affected by magic) aadmi hai
  26,154,"Tu hum jaise ek Insaan ke siwa aur kya hai, laa koi nishani agar tu saccha hai”"
  26,155,Saleh ne kaha “yeh ountni (she-camel) hai ek din iske peene ka hai aur ek din tum sab ke pani lenay ka
  26,156,Isko hargiz na chedhna(molest) warna ek baday din ka azaab tumko aa lega”
  26,157,Magar unhon ne iski kunchein kaat di (hamstrung her) aur aakhir-e-kaar pachtate reh gaye
  26,158,"Azaab ne unhein aa liya, yaqeenan ismein ek nishani hai, magar in mein se aksar maanne waley nahin"
  26,159,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi
  26,160,Lut ki qaum ne Rasoolon ko jhutlaya
  26,161,Yaad karo jabke unke bhai Lut ne unsey kaha tha “kya tum darte nahin
  26,162,Main tumhare liye ek amanat-daar Rasool hoon
  26,163,Lihaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,164,"Main is kaam par tumse kisi ajar ka talib nahin hoon, mera ajar to Rabbul aalameen ke zimme hai"
  26,165,Kya tum duniya ki makhlooq mein se Mardon ke paas jatey ho
  26,166,Aur tumhari biwiyon mein tumhare Rubb ne tumhare liye jo kuch paida kiya hai usey chodh detey ho? Balke tum log to hadd se hi guzar gaye ho.”
  26,167,Unhon ne kaha “ aey Lut” agar tu in baaton se baaz na aaya to jo log hamari bastiyon se nikale gaye hain unmein tu bhi shamil ho kar rahega”
  26,168,Usne kaha “tumhare kartooton par jo log kudd (abhor/detest) rahey hain main un mein shamil hoon
  26,169,"Aey parwardigar, mujhey aur mere ehal-o-ayaal (me and my people/ my family) ko inki badkirdariyon se nijaat de”"
  26,170,Aakhir e kaar humne usey aur uske sab ehal-o-ayaal ko bacha liya
  26,171,Bajuz ek budiya ke jo peechey reh janey walon mein se thi
  26,172,Phir baaqi maanda(rest) logon ko humne tabaah kardiya
  26,173,"Aur unpar barsayi ek barsaat, badi hi buri baarish thi jo un daraye janey walon par nazil hui"
  26,174,"Yaqeenan ismein ek nishani hai, magar inmein se aksar maanne waley nahin"
  26,175,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi
  26,176,Ashaab-ul-Aiyqah ne Rasoolon ko jhutlaya
  26,177,Yaad karo jabke Shoaib ne unse kaha tha “kya tum darte nahin
  26,178,Main tumhare liye ek amanat-daar Rasool hoon
  26,179,Lihaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,180,"Main is kaam par tumse kisi ajar ka talib nahin hoon, mera ajar to Rabbul aalameen ke zimme hai"